-- Euro Finance Chiefs to Meet November 20 on Greece, Juncker Says
-- B y   D a r a   D o y l e
-- 2012-11-12T22:26:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-12/euro-finance-chiefs-to-meet-november-20-on-greece-juncker-says.html
Euro-area finance ministers will
meet again Nov. 20 to discuss  Greece , Luxembourg’s Prime
Minister Jean- Claude Juncker, who heads the group of euro-area
finance ministers, told reporters in Brussels.  “Together with the review of the Greek adjustment program
the eurogroup will further discuss financing needs and debt
sustainability at an extraordinary meeting that will be convened
on 20 November,” the ministers said in a statement, read out by
Juncker.    To contact the editor responsible for this story:
